text: Watercolors is the seventh studio album by American indie solo project Ducktails, released on June 21, 2019. == Reception == Section26, a French music review website, gave a positive review of the album ending it with, "a poor guy wrote a great album". == Track listing == == References == Category:2019 albums Category:Ducktails (band) albums
title: Watercolors (Ducktails album)
